      <p>An <a href="ch70s07.html#MonstersO-R67">owlbear's</a> coat ranges in color from brown-black to yellowish brown; its beak is a dull ivory color. A full-grown male can stand as tall as 8 feet and weigh up to 1,500 pounds. Adventurers who have survived encounters with the creature often speak of the bestial madness they glimpsed in its red-rimmed eyes.<a href="img/MonstersO-R.Owlbear.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersO-R.Owlbear.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2127139"/>Combat</h5>
