        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">monsterinfo</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R68"/>
        <p><a href="ch70s07.html#MonstersO-R67">Owlbears</a> attack prey-any creature bigger than a mouse-on sight, always fighting to the death. They slash with claws and beak, trying to grab their prey and rip it apart.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2127171"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R69"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Improved Grab (Ex):</strong></span> To use this ability, an <a href="ch70s07.html#MonstersO-R67">owlbear</a> must hit with a claw attack. It can then attempt to start a grapple as a free action without provoking an attack of opportunity.</p>
